column5: And another ice fishing trip planned for tomorrow. Got to load the sled on the trailer now that the roads are pretty much ice free.Hope to have the boat out for some spring cleaning and work in a couple of weeks. Be a few more before I get it wet though.
Sunny and 22 here today, and the crappies are on fire!!  No drilling required
4'-5' of ice with 0'-3' of snow on top here.
Lovin life eh D?   Seriously though it is pretty cool you are ice fishin still
